1:
Ascribe to Yahweh, you sons of God,\q ascribe to Yahweh glory and strength!
\q
2:
Ascribe to Yahweh the glory his name deserves.\q Bow down to Yahweh in the splendor of holiness!


\q
3:
The voice of Yahweh is heard over the waters;\q the God of glory thunders,
\q Yahweh thunders over many waters.
\q
4:
The voice of Yahweh is powerful;\q the voice of Yahweh is majestic.
\q
5:
The voice of Yahweh breaks the cedars;\q Yahweh breaks in pieces the cedars of Lebanon.


\q
6:
He makes Lebanon skip like a calf\q and Sirion like a young ox.
\q
7: The voice of Yahweh sends out flames of fire.\q
8:
The voice of Yahweh shakes the wilderness;\q Yahweh shakes the wilderness of Kadesh.


\q
9:
The voice of Yahweh causes the oaks to twist\q and strips the forests bare.
\q Everyone in his temple says, "Glory!"
\q
10:
Yahweh sits as king over the flood;\q Yahweh sits as king forever.


\q
11: Yahweh gives strength to his people;\q Yahweh blesses his people with peace.
